metadata.name: Janus
metadata.description:
In Roman mythology, Janus is the god of change and transitions. People usually fear change, but we need to move on letting go of but not forgetting the past. For the sake of future generations, we need to keep learning about the past and keep passing on our heritage. So, letâ€™s make a big move in the new year having in mind all the precious things we leave behind!
